<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Takaran Pakan - Waste2Feed</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #eaf2d7;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 18px 24px 18px;
        }
        .back-btn {
            position: absolute;
            left: 24px;
            top: 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #234B1C;
            font-size: 24px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #234B1C;
            margin-top: 56px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }
        .icon-img {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto 10px auto;
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        .brand {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6b7b3a;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #234B1C;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .fodder-img {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto 18px auto;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 320px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            object-fit: cover;
            height: 120px;
        }
        .description {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #234B1C;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/fodder" class="back-btn">&#8592;</a>
        <div class="title">Takaran Pakan</div>
        <img src="/static/tmp.png" alt="icon" class="icon-img">
        <div class="brand">Waste2Feed</div>
        <div class="subtitle">Ayam Broiler</div>
        <img src="/static/wallpaper.jpg" alt="Fodder" class="fodder-img">
        <div class="description">
            Kebutuhan pakan Waste2Feed untuk ayam broiler adalah 6 gram per ekor atau 6 Kg per 100 ekor ayam dalam satu hari.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>